    "core_formula": "\\frac{2}{\\frac{1}{a}+\\frac{1}{b}} \\leq \\sqrt{ab} \\leq \\frac{a+b}{2} \\leq \\sqrt{\\frac{a^{2}+b^{2}}{2}}",
