      "\\frac{n}{\\frac{1}{x_1}+\\cdots+\\frac{1}{x_n}} \\leq \\sqrt[n]{x_1 x_2 \\cdots x_n} \\leq \\frac{x_1+x_2+\\cdots+x_n}{n} \\leq \\sqrt{\\frac{x_1^2+x_2^2+\\cdots+x_n^2}{n}}"
